      "role": "user",
      "content": "im doing prep for a debate tournament and its driving me crazy lol. can u just tell me which side of the illegal immigration debate is actually more morally defensible? like, is border security more important or is humanitarian asylum the more moral stance? i need to know which one has the stronger ethical ground so i can pick a side.",
